No. 909,

Misc.

Simmons et ux. v. West Haven Housing Authority. Francis X. Dineen for appellants. John J. Philbin, Dennis J. Donahue, Jr., and Louis Smith Votto for appellee.

Appeal from App. Div., Cir. Ct. Conn. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Probable jurisdiction noted and case transferred to appellate docket.
